<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmed - CarRental</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #374151;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a, #15803d);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .booking-details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #16a34a;
        }
        
        .booking-details h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .detail-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .vehicle-info {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .vehicle-info h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #15803d;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .vehicle-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .important-info {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .important-info h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .important-info ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .important-info li {
            padding: 5px 0;
            color: #92400e;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .important-info li:before {
            content: "âš ";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A11312, #8a0f0e);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .contact-info p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .agent-info {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .agent-info p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .detail-grid, .vehicle-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">ðŸš— CarRental</div>
            <h1>Booking Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>Your car rental has been confirmed by the agent</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello <%= customerName %>! ðŸŽ‰
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Great news! Your booking has been confirmed by the vehicle owner. 
                Your car rental is now confirmed and ready for your trip.
            </div>
            
            <div class="booking-details">
                <h3>Booking Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-grid">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Booking ID</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= bookingId %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Status</div>
                        <div class="detail-value" style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600;">Confirmed</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Pickup Date</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= pickupDate %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Return Date</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= returnDate %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Total Price</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">KSH <%= totalPrice %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Pickup Location</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= pickupLocation %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="vehicle-info">
                <h3>Vehicle Information</h3>
                <div class="vehicle-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Vehicle</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= vehicleMake %> <%= vehicleModel %> (<%= vehicleYear %>)</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">License Plate</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= licensePlate %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Color</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= vehicleColor %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Fuel Type</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= fuelType %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="important-info">
                <h3>Important Information</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Please arrive on time for pickup</li>
                    <li>Bring your driver's license and booking confirmation</li>
                    <li>Inspect the vehicle before driving</li>
                    <li>Return the vehicle in the same condition</li>
                    <li>Contact the agent if you have any issues</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <a href="<%= bookingUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                View Booking Details
            </a>
            
            <div class="message">
                Have a great trip! If you need any assistance during your rental, 
                don't hesitate to contact the vehicle owner or our support team.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><strong>The CarRental Team</strong></p>
            
            <div class="agent-info">
                <p><strong>Vehicle Owner:</strong> <%= agentName %></p>
                <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <%= agentEmail %></p>
                <% if (agentPhone) { %>
                    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= agentPhone %></p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <h4>Need Help?</h4>
                <p>Email: carrent@info.com</p>
                <p>Phone: 0768163367</p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
                This email was sent to <%= customerEmail %>. If you have any questions, please contact our support team.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 